        {
            "id": 6007224,
            "title": "蘋果遭Needham降評 AI競爭與成長疑慮加劇",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據《彭博》周三 (4 日) 報導，Needham 將蘋果 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>) 評等從「買進」下調至「持有」，顯示華爾街對其成長前景與在人工智慧 (AI) 領域的地位感到憂慮。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007224%2Fl%2Fe9f9425aa4b75e7dd582b0668ce80dd1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">蘋果股價今年以來已下跌約17%，成為「美股科技七雄」中表現最差的股票。</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Needham 分析師 Laura Martin 指出多項風險，包括競爭和成長趨緩，以及估值「在多項指標上看起來都很昂貴」。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截稿前，蘋果股價在盤前交易中下跌 0.4%，暫報 202.45 美元。換算該股今年已下跌約 17%，成為「美股科技七雄」中表現最差的股票。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雖然蘋果大部分賣壓反映了政治不確定性，因為該公司被視為特別容易受到關稅衝擊，且因其全球製造布局屢遭川普政府點名批評。不過，它在 AI 領域的困境也是另一個重大拖累因素。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>「這檔股票要有表現，必須要有 iPhone 換機週期的催化劑，而我們預期未來 12 個月內不會出現，」Martin 寫道，並補充道，蘋果在生成式 AI 的創新上一直較為落後，為可能威脅 iOS 設備的新硬體型態開啟了大門。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>OpenAI 最近宣布收購由蘋果傳奇設計師艾夫 (Jony Ive) 共同創辦的 AI 裝置新創 io。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今年以來，已有多間機構下調蘋果評等，包含 Oppenheimer、MoffettNathanson、Loop Capital、Aletheia Capital 和星展銀行，5 月的 Jefferies 和 Rosenblatt Securities，Needham 是最新加入看淡蘋果行列的機構。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>目前，彭博追蹤的分析師中只有不到 60% 建議買進該股，這在大型股中是相當低的比例。微軟 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)、亞馬遜 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)、輝達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 和 Meta(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:META:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/META\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">META-US</a>) 的買進建議比例都接近或超過 90%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6007224",
